# Wiki index for {{owner.name}}

This file lists every page in `personal/wiki/` with a one-line summary.
{{assistant_name}} reads this on every new session to decide which other
pages might be relevant to the current message.

## Always-loaded pages (loaded automatically on new session)

- `identity.md` — durable identity context for {{owner.name}}.
- `principles.md` — working principles and trade-offs.

## On-demand pages

Use this section as you create more wiki pages. Format:
`path/page.md` — one-line summary of what it covers.

(empty — populate as the wiki grows)

## Strategic context

The harness also loads, on every new session, anything in
`personal/wiki/follow-ups.md`, `personal/wiki/open-questions.md`, and
any decision files in `personal/wiki/decisions/` modified in the last
7 days. Use those for active threads; use this index for durable topic
pages.
